---
---
<section class="relative isolate bg-deep-teal text-warm-gray py-24 sm:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- background image -->
  <img
    src="/images/arch/mission.jpg"
    alt=""
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 w-full h-full object-cover duotone opacity-25"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-deep-teal via-deep-teal/85 to-deep-teal"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 blueprint-grid opacity-30"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-sand/40 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-5 sm:px-8 text-center">
    <p class="eyebrow text-sand mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-3" data-reveal>
      <span class="inline-block w-9 h-px bg-sand rule-draw"></span>
      Our mission
      <span class="inline-block w-9 h-px bg-sand"></span>
    </p>

    <blockquote
      class="font-display font-medium text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2.6rem] leading-[1.32] text-warm-gray"
      data-reveal
      style="--reveal-delay:120ms"
    >
      To transform our clients' ideas into{' '}
      <span class="text-sand">functional, high-impact architectural solutions</span>{' '}
      through specialized design, modeling and technical development of steel
      and glass products.
    </blockquote>

    <p class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-warm-gray/70" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay:240ms">
      We are the strategic ally of architects, builders and clients looking to
      transform their spaces with solid, modern products built to last —
      connecting design vision with results that convey trust, durability and
      value.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
